title: There IS Evidence of Fraud, But You Have to Open Your Eyes (Ep 1406)
description:
In this episode, I discuss the stunning new voter fraud allegations emerging out of this key swing state. I also address the Project Veritas CNN bombshell. 

News Picks:


CNN caught on tape burying the Hunter Biden story. 

Stunning new voter fraud allegations emerge out of Nevada.

Sidney Powell gets an expedited appeal in Georgia in the Dominion voting machines audit case.


Twitter and Fakebook melt down over President Trump’s White House speech.


Media rushes to defend Biden staffer over communist hammer and sickle hat. 

Wikipedia embarrasses itself again!
